Adobe Acrobat's PDF-to-EPUB conversion is available only in the Pro version. It costs around $23/month as part of an Acrobat subscription. The conversion quality is good for text-heavy PDFs but can struggle with complex layouts. Multi-column text may not reflow properly in the resulting EPUB.

